# Walkthrough: Repo Evolution Pipeline Restructuring

I have completed a comprehensive audit and restructuring of the **repo-evolution-pipeline**. The project is now clean, fully tested, and functional for end-to-end mobile app generation.

## 🛠️ Key Improvements

### 1. Legacy Code Removal (V1 → V2)
Deleted **12 obsolete files** from the V1 LangGraph prototype that were causing import confusion and duplicating state models.
- Removed `/agents/`, `/graph/`, `/api/`, and `/tests/` (V1).
- Unified the system under the `pipeline/` (V2) architecture.

### 2. Schema Normalization
Fixed **15+ Pydantic schema mismatches** that prevented data from flowing between agents.
- **Models**: Added missing fields (`topics`, `complexity_score`, `design_tokens`, etc.) to [RepoManifest](file:///Users/mkazi/GitLab%20Mobile%20/repo-evolution-pipeline/pipeline/core/models.py#77-97) and [DeepAnalysis](file:///Users/mkazi/GitLab%20Mobile%20/repo-evolution-pipeline/pipeline/core/models.py#99-122).
- **Enums**: Expanded [RepoCategory](file:///Users/mkazi/GitLab%20Mobile%20/repo-evolution-pipeline/pipeline/core/models.py#17-30) and [NavigationType](file:///Users/mkazi/GitLab%20Mobile%20/repo-evolution-pipeline/pipeline/core/models.py#39-45) to match LLM-generated output.
- **Quality Gates**: Standardized the [QualityGate](file:///Users/mkazi/GitLab%20Mobile%20/repo-evolution-pipeline/pipeline/core/models.py#171-182) model to track [passed](file:///Users/mkazi/GitLab%20Mobile%20/repo-evolution-pipeline/pipeline/tests/test_models.py#95-105) status and `weight`.

### 3. Agent & Core Fixes
- **LLM Client**: Added [.env](file:///Users/mkazi/GitLab%20Mobile%20/repo-evolution-pipeline/.env) loading via `python_dotenv` for seamless local/background execution.
- **Codegen**: Fixed the [invoke_with_retry](file:///Users/mkazi/GitLab%20Mobile%20/repo-evolution-pipeline/pipeline/core/llm.py#149-202) bug where it attempted to parse React Native code as JSON.
- **Scanner**: Updated route extraction to correctly handle Next.js root routes (`/`).
- **Packaging**: Renamed `design-system` to [design_system](file:///Users/mkazi/GitLab%20Mobile%20/repo-evolution-pipeline/pipeline/quality/gates.py#372-390) to fix Python import errors.

